# Administrative Hierarchy (Nepal Context)

Issues and users are tagged with administrative levels for scoping:

Province → District → Municipality (Palika) → Ward

All issues must store:

* wardNumber
* municipalityName
* districtName
* provinceName

All users (except CITIZEN) must have their jurisdiction set on their profile.

Scoping rules:

* CITIZEN: can submit from any location, views issues in their ward
* LOCAL_BODY_EMPLOYEE: scoped to their municipalityName
* LOCAL_BODY_HEAD: scoped to their municipalityName
* EXECUTIVE_BODY: no scope restriction — sees everything

