# Primary Workflow

Citizen submits report -> AI categorizes + checks for duplicates -> Report attaches to existing Issue OR creates new Issue -> Community verifies issue (3 verifications OR LOCAL_BODY_HEAD manual) -> Issue assigned to LOCAL_BODY_EMPLOYEE by LOCAL_BODY_HEAD -> Employee investigates -> Employee uploads updates -> Employee marks resolved -> Citizen + community verify resolution -> Issue closed OR Issue reopened

If AI detects root cause pattern across 3+ related issues -> Suggestion stored on each Issue -> LOCAL_BODY_HEAD reviews suggestion -> Accepts/edits/rejects -> Root Issue created and issues linked

