# Architecture Principles

Keep architecture simple.

Do NOT introduce:

* Microservices
* Message queues
* Background workers or cron jobs
* Redis or any cache layer
* Separate AI service

This is a hackathon MVP.

Prefer:

* Simple APIs
* Clear database models
* Fast implementation
* Strong demo experience

Escalation is computed on page load, not via background jobs.
AI calls are made synchronously during report submission.
No webhooks, no polling, no websockets.

